{
  "doc_id": "17717",
  "text": "The amount of nitrite (NO 2 − ) present in the supernatants was measured as an indicator of NO production using the Griess method [CITATION_1] . The amount of NO 2 − in the supernatants was calculated using a standard curve with serial NaNO 2 dilutions. The assay was performed in quadruplicate, and the absorbance at 540 nm was recorded 10 min after addition of NaNO 2 .",
